<p>今日LOL测试服整体改动不多，主要是天使莉莉娅加强，6款新皮肤发布！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LOL英雄改动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200805/522eb23441b0478f89589c2134754c00.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>正义天使 凯尔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>W-星界恩典</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▼法力值消耗由70/80/90/100/110提升到90/100/110/120/130。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>E-星火符刃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▲冷却时间由8秒降低到8/7.5/7/6.5/6秒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▲法力值消耗由50/55/60/65/70调整为无消耗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>含羞蓓蕾 莉莉娅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>Q-大杀四方(</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">▲对小兵的伤害效率百分比由50%提升到80%。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>云顶之弈改动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>破法者</strong></p>
<p>提升目标下一次施法所需要的的法力值消耗的比例由40%降低到33%。</p>
